data.description: MAJOR PRICE IMPROVEMENT. Welcome home to this MOVE-IN-READY BEAUTY located in the highly sought-after community of Rivers Reach. Situated on an over-sized private lot in the community and features a HUGE fence-able backyard, perfect for that perfect dream pool, outdoor entertaining and/or pet's delight. With an open floor plan that boasts four spacious bedrooms, two baths, a large den/office, and an amazing bonus space upstairs, there's ample room for everyone. The master bedroom is tucked away towards the back of the home, providing a quiet and peaceful space, while the remaining bedrooms are situated up front in their own private hallway. The kitchen/dining room/great room combo is perfect for everyday living and entertainment. With tons of natural light, this kitchen features modern quartz counter tops, bright cabinets, double oven, French door refrigerator, and tons of storage. The main interior layout features a beautiful custom ship lap wall, recessed canned lighting, and ample windows, providing natural light throughout the home. Enjoy the light and bright master bedroom featuring a large WIC, custom barn door leading into the master bath, complete with dual vanities, private water closet, and plenty of storage. Rivers Reach provides easy access to Shopping, Dining, I75, State Road 64, Lakewood Ranch, stunning Gulf Beaches, Sarasota, Tampa, St. Pete, Airports and more. Everything is within reach in Rivers Reach.  Community amenities include a resort style pool, spa, fitness area, an outdoor kitchen/grill area, playground, sand volleyball court community kayak storage and access to the Manatee River. Call to schedule your showing today, you will not be disappointed! ** CDD is included in Taxes.
